---
title: Seared Salmon & Kale Salad with Mango Tangy Avocado Dressing, Tomato, Scallion
description: This colorful salad is the perfect day-off meal for any mom in your life, ready in just 15 minutes. You’ll sear salmon and serve it atop kale salad with juicy tomato and mango in a creamy, tangy avocado dressing brightened up with a splash of mango juice. With a garnish of zippy scallion greens and squeeze of lemon, your work is done—and the grade? A+!
